              <h2>Let's Explore the Most Popular Folktales Across The World!</h2>
              <p>
                <span>Folktales</span></a> are traditional stories that are passed <br>
                down orally from generation to generation. They are created by "the folks"<br>
                or the people, and often feature magical or supernatural elements. These stories <br>
                can explain something or provide moral lessons. They are ussually fictional <br>
                and may involve talking animals, royalty, peasants, or mythical creatures.
              </p>
              <h3>So today you can:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Learn some more about the Folktales</li>
              <li>Learn something new from those stories</li>
              <li>To get know what Folktales are the most popular around the world</li>
              <li>To learn some good morals out of the folklore</li>
            </ul>
